    "body": "When connecting to other nodes, we have several channels open against them in order to improve perf, and control different characteristics of channels (some used for recovery, others used for ping). The unicast discovery does an initial connection to nodes and then disconnects from them, so this type of connection should be more lightweight.\n", 
